{"tid":1581460,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"對今次革命信心開始動搖既人，有時間不坊睇下呢套戲","createTime":"2019-09-19T14:39:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-19T17:03:37.000Z","uid":246520,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"25e56e4272f28b62e7ddda6ad929a7a1474192f8","tid":1581460,"uid":246520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T14:39:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/I/41QST6DYNDL._SX383_BO1,204,203,200_.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-na.ssl-images-amazon.com%2Fimages%2FI%2F41QST6DYNDL._SX383_BO1%2C204%2C203%2C200_.jpg&h=9b03d97e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/thumb/1/11/V_for_Vendetta.jpg/220px-V_for_Vendetta.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fthumb%2F1%2F11%2FV_for_Vendetta.jpg%2F220px-V_for_Vendetta.jpg&h=9737f5bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係一個受到絕對強權統治、處於一個異見人士、同性戀等會俾政府捉走囚禁、反對意見完全被抑壓既社會，主角V獨自走出黎譴責同公開政府既暴行，用佢既文宣逐漸喚醒人民，約定大家係一年後既某一日企出黎推翻政府。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">到左個日，人民帶住V既面罩一齊行出黎，軍隊不敵人民、強權成功被推翻，最後所有人係議會大廈前除低面罩。<br />\n<br />\nV犧牲自己，為人民帶黎一個新既世界。</span><br />\n<br />\nWho was he?<br />\nHe was Edmond Dantes.<br />\nAnd he was my father...<br />\n...and my mother.<br />\nMy brother.<br />\nMy friend.<br />\nHe was you...<br />\n...and me.<br />\nHe was all of us.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>集眾人之力，<br />\n我地今次一定要贏。<br />\n一定會贏！</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/gZfvwNdXjfc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FgZfvwNdXjfc&d=kSOQn%2BAsZtDywzIR1u7IP%2FTmwccdIWYcDO8ZGhePZ24%3D&h=d532ea1f\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/gZfvwNdXjfc</a>"},{"pid":"1c616652067ca192fbbaa673843b50a7e9bc2912","tid":1581460,"uid":271234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20